# IG / video binaries — keep them out of the public repo (CTK-166 leak guard).
# The IG *code* belongs here; rendered reels, captured frames, and mirrored vendor
# photos pulled for posting do NOT. Reels default to build/reels (already covered by
# /build above + uploaded as GH Actions run artifacts); pulled photos / working assets
# land in the gitignored dirs below. Scoped on purpose — no global *.png/*.webp, so the
# tracked assets/brand/ build assets stay versioned.
/ig-assets/
/.ig-work/
*.mp4
*.mov
